hadiths[118]{hadithnumber,text}:
1395,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman (ka Hakim bana kar) bheja to farmaya ke tum unhein us kalime ki gawahi ki dawat dena ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur ye ke main Allah ka rasool hun. agar wo log ye baat maan lein to phir unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne un par rozaana panch waqt ki namazein farz ki hain. agar wo log ye baat bhi maan lein to phir unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unke maal par kuchh sadqa farz kya hai jo unke maaldaar logon se lekar unhiin ke mohtajon mein lota diya jaeyga
1396,aik shakhs ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke aap mujhey koi aisa amal bataiye jo mujhey jannat mein ley jaey. is par logon ne kaha ke aakhir ye kya chahta hai. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to bahut aham zarurat hai. ( suno ( Allah ki ibadat karo aur uska koi Sharik na thahraao. Namaz qaaim karo. zakat do aur sila rehmii karo aur Behaz ne kaha ke ham se Shoba ne bayan kya ke ham se Muhammad-bin Usman aur unke bap Usman bin-Abdullah ne bayan kya ke un donon saahibon ne Musa-bin-Talha se suna aur unhon-ne Abu-Ayub se aur unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki tarah ( suna ( abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke mujhey dar hai ke Muhammad se riwayat ghair mehfooz hai aur riwayat Amr-bin-Usmaan se (mahfooz hai).
1397,"aik dehati Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha ke aap mujhey koi aisa kaam batlaaiye jis par agar main hameshgii karun to jannat mein dakhil ho jaun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ki ibadat kar, uska kisi ko Sharik na thahraa, farz Namaz qaaim kar, farz zakat de aur Ramazan ke rozey rakh. dehati ne kaha us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai, un amalon par main koi zyadti nahi karunga . jab wo peeth mod kar janey laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar koi aisey shakhs ko dekhnaa chahey jo jannat walon mein se ho to wo us shakhs ko dekh ley."
1398,"qabila abdul-Qais ka wafad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah! ham qabila Rabee ki aik shaakh hain aur qabila Muzar ke kaafir hamarey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darmyan padtey hain. isliye ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein sirf hurmat ke mahinon hi mein hazir ho saktey hain (kyonke un mahinon mein ladaaiyaan band ho jati hain aur rastey pur-amn ho jatey hain) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hamein kuchh aisi baatein batla dijiye jis par ham khud bhi amal karein aur apne qabeele ke logon se bhi un par amal karne ke liye kahin jo hamarey sath nahi aa sakey hain. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumhen char baton ka hukm deta hun aur char chizon se roktaa hun. Allah Taala par eman laney aur uski whdaniyat ki shahadat dene ka (ye kehtey huey) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungli se aik taraf ishara kya. Namaz qaaim karnaa, phir zakat ada karna aur maale-ghanimat se panchwan hissey ada karne (ka hukm deta hun) aur main tumhen kaddu ki tonbi se aur hantam (sabz rang ka chhota sa martban jaisa ghadaa) faqeer (khajoor ki jad se khodaa hua aik bartan) aur zuft laga hua bartan (zuft Basra mein aik qism ka tel hota tha) ke istemal se mana karta hun. Sulaiman aur Abu-Naumaan ne Hammad ke waaste se yahi riwayat is tarah bayan ki hai. (الإيمان بالله شهادة أن لا إله إلا الله) yaanii Allah par eman laney ka matlab ( لا إله إلا الله ( ki gawahi dena."
1399,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) faut ho gaey aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khaleefa huey to Arab ke kuchh qabaayel kaafir ho gaey (aur kuchh ne zakat se inkar kar diya aur Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse ladna chaahaa) to umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us farman ki maujoodgii mein kyonkar jang kar saktey hain'' mujhey hukm hai logon se us waqt tak jang karun jab tak ke wo ( لا إله إلا الله ( ki shahadat na de dein aur jo shakhs uski shahadat de-dey to meri taraf se iska maal aur jaan mehfooz ho jaeyga siwaay usi ke haq ke (yani qisaas wghaira ki Suraton ke) aur iska hisab Allah Taala ke zimme hoga.
1400,"qism Allah ki main har us shakhs se jang karunga jo zakat aur Namaz mein tafreeq karega. (yani Namaz to padhey magar zakat ke liye inkar kar de) kyonke zakat maal ka haq hai. Allah ki qasam! agar unhon-ne zakat mein char mahiney ki (bakrii ke) bachchey ko dene se bhi inkar kya jisey wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko detey they, to main unse ladunga. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke ba-khuda ye baat iska nateeja thi ke Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ka Sina Islam ke liye khol diya tha aur baad mein, main bhi us nateeje par pahuncha ke Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hi haq par they."
1401,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Namaz qaaim karne, zakat dene aur har musalman ke sath khair-khuwaahii karne par bait ki thi."
1402,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke oont (qiyamat ke din) apne maalikon ke paas jinhoney unka haq (zakaat) na ada kya ke us se zyada motey taazey ho kar aaeingey (jaisey duniya mein they) aur unhein apne khuron se raundengey. bakriyan bhi apne un maalikon ke paas jinhonne unke haq nahi diye they pahley se zyada motii taazii ho kar aaeingii aur unhein apne khuron se raundengii aur apne seengon se maarengii. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke uska haq ye bhi hai ke usey pani hi par (yani jahan wo charaagaah mein char rahi hon) dohaa jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi shakhs qiyamat ke din is tarah na aaey ke wo apni gardan par aik aisi bakri uthaey huey ho jo chilla rahi ho aur wo (shakhs) mujh se kahey ke aey Muhammad (sl)! mujhey azab se bachaaiye main usey ye jawab doonga ke terey liye main kuchh nahi kar sakta (meraa kaam pahunchaanaa tha) so maine pahuncha diya. isi tarah koi shakhs apni gardan par oont liye huey qiyamat ke din na aaey ke oont chilla raha ho aur wo khud mujh se faryaad karey, aey Muhammad (sl)! mujhey bachaaiye aur main ye jawab de dun ke terey liye main kuchh nahi kar sakta. maine tujh ko) Allah ka hukme-zakaat) pahuncha diya tha."
1403,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisey Allah ne maal diya aur usne uski zakat nahi ada ki to qiyamat ke din iska maal bahut hi zyada zahreeley ganjey sanp ki shakl ikhtiyar kar lega. uski aankhon ke paas 2 siyah nuqtey hongey. jaisey sanp ke hotey hain, phir wo sanp iske donon jabdon se usey pakad lega aur kahega ke main tera maal aur khazaana hun. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye aayat padhii'' aur wo log ye guman na karein ke Allah Taala ne unhein jo kuchh apne Fazal se diya hai wo is par kanjoosii se kaam letey hain ke unka maal unke liye behtar hai. balke wo bura hai jis maal ke maamle mein unhon-ne kanjoosii kya hai. qiyamat mein iska tauq bana kar unki gardan mein daala jaaeyga.''"
1404,"ham Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath kahin ja rahe they. aik dehati ne aap se puchha ke mujhey Allah Taala ke us farman ki tafseer batlaaiye, jo log soney aur chandi ka khazaana bana kar rakhtey hain. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne iska jawab diya ke agar kisi ne sonaa-chaandii jama kya aur uski zakat na di to uske liye (kharaabii) hai. ye hukm zakat ke ehkaam nazil honey se pahley tha lekin jab Allah Taala ne zakat ka hukm nazil kar diya to ab wahi zakat maal w daulat ko paak kar dene wali hai."
1405,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya panch auqiya se kam chandi mein zakat nahi hai aur panch oonton se kam mein zakat nahi hai aur panch wasq se kam (ghalle) mein zakat nahi hai.
1406,mein maqam Rabza se guzar raha tha ke Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) dikhai diye. maine puchha ke aap yahan kyon aagey hain? unhon-ne jawab diya ke main Sham (Syria) mein tha to Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se mera ikhtilaf ( Quran ki aayat ( ''jo log sona aur chandi jama kartey hain aur unhein Allah ki raah mein kharch nahi kartey '' ke mutaalliq ho gaya. Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ka kehna ye tha ke ye aayat ahle-kitab ke barey mein nazil hui hai aur main ye kehta tha ke ahle-kitab ke sath hamarey mutaalliq bhi ye nazil hui hai. us ikhtilaf ke nateeja mein mere aur unke darmyan kuchh khataas paida ho gaee. chunanche unhon-ne Usman (Raziallahu anhu) (jo un dinon musalmaanon ke liye bahut meharbaan they) ke yahan meri shikayat likhi. Usman (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey likha ke main Madina chala aaoon. chunanche main chala aaya. (wahaan jab pahunchaa) to logon ka mere yahan is tarah hujoom honey laga jaisey unhon-ne mujhey pahley dekha hi na ho. phir jab maine logon ke is tarah apni taraf aaney ke mutaalliq Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha to unhon-ne farmaya ke agar munasib samjho to yahan ka qiyam chhod kar Madina se qareeb hi kahin aur jagah alag qiyam ikhtiyar kar lo. yahi baat hai jo mujhey yahan (Rabza) tak ley aai hai. agar wo mere uper aik habshi ko bhi ameer muqarrar kar dein to main uski bhi sununga aur itaat karunga.
1407,"main betha tha (doosri sanad) aur imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne farmaya ke mujh se Ishaq-bin-Mansur ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke ham se Abdus-Samad-bin-abdul-waaris ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha ke mujh se mere bap ne bayan kya, unhon-ne kaha mujh se Saeed Jurairi ne bayan kya, kaha ke ham se Abul-Alaa-bin-shikhkhiir ne bayan kya, unse ahnaf-bin-Qais ne bayan kya ke main Quraish ki aik majlis mein betha hua tha. itney mein sakht baal, motey kapdey aur motii-jhotii haalat mein aik shakhs aaya aur khadey ho kar salam kya aur kaha ke khazaana jama karne walon ko us patthar ki bashaarat ho jo jahannam ki aag mein tapaayaa jaeyga aur uski chhaatii ki bhatni par rakh diya jaeyga jo mundhey ki taraf se paar ho jaeyga is tarah wo patthar barabar dhalaktaa rahega. ye keh kar wo sahib chaley gaey aur aik sutoon ke paas tak laga kar baith gaey. mein bhi unke sath chala aur unke qareeb baith gaya. ab tak mujhey ye malum na tha ke ye kon sahib hain. maine unse kaha ke mera khayal hai ke aap ki baat qaum ne pasand nahi ki. unhon-ne kaha ye sab to bewaqoof hain."
1408,us waqt maine suraj ki taraf nazar utha kar dekha ke kitna din abhi baqi hai. kyonke mujhey (aap ki baat se) ye khayal guzra ke aap apne kisi kaam ke liye mujhey bhejengey. maine jawab diya ke ji haan (Uhud pahaad maine dekha hai) aap ne farmaya ke agar mere paas Uhud pahaad ke barabar sona ho mein iske siwa dost nahi rakhta ke sirf teen Dinar bacha kar baqi tamam ka tamam ( Allah ke rastey mein) de daalun (abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir farmaya ke) un logon ko kuchh malum nahi ye duniya jama karne ki fikr kartey hain. hargiz nahi Allah ki qism na main unki duniya unse mangta hun aur na Deen ka koi masla unse poochhta hun yahan tak ke main Allah Taala se ja miloon.
1409,hasad ( rashk ( karna sirf 2 hi aadmiyon ke sath jaaiz ho sakta hai. aik to us shakhs ke sath jisey Allah ne maal diya aur usey haq aur munasib jaghon mein kharch karne ki taufeeq di. doosrey us shakhs ke sath jisey Allah Taala ne hikmat (aql ilm Quran w hadis aur mamla fahmii) di aur wo apni hikmat ke mutabiq haq faisley karta hai aur logon ko uski taleem deta hai.
1410,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs halal kamaaii se aik khajoor ke barabar sadqa karey aur Allah Taala sirf halal kamaaii ke sadqe ko qabool karta hai to Allah Taala usey apne daahiney hath se qabool karta hai phir sadqa karne waley ke faaydey ke liye usmein zyadti karta hai. bilkul isi tarah jaisey koi apne janwar ke bachchey ko khilaa-pilaa kar badhata hai yahan tak ke uska sadqa pahaad ke barabar ho jata hai. Abdur-Rehman ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Sulaiman ne Abdullaah-bin-Diinaar ki riwayat se ki hai aur Warqaa ne ibne-diinaar se kaha, unse Saeed-bin-Yasaar ne, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aur uski riwayat Muslim-bin-abii-Maryam, Zaid-bin-Aslam aur Suhel ne Abu-Saleh se ki, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne."
1411,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna tha ke sadqe karo, aik aisa zamana bhi tum par aaney wala hai jab aik shakhs apne maal ka sadqa lekar niklega aur koi usey qabool karne wala nahi paaeyga."
1412,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya qiyamat aaney se pahley maal w daulat ki is qadr kasarat ho jaeygi aur log is qadr maaldaar ho jaeinge ke us waqt saahibe-maal ko uski fikr hogi ke uski zakat kon qabool karey aur agar kisi ko dena bhi chaahega to usko ye jawab milega ke mujhey uski haajat nahi hai.
1413,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein maujood tha ke 2 log aaey, aik faqr w faaqe ki shikayat liye huey tha aur doosrey ko raston ke ghair mehfooz honey ki shikayat thi. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jahan tak raston ke ghair mehfooz honey ka talluq hai to bahut jald aisa zamana aaney wala hai ke jab aik qaafila Makka se kisi muhaafiz ke baghair niklega. (aur usey rastey mein koi khatrah na hoga) aur raha faqr w faaqa to qiyamat us waqt tak nahi aaeygii jab tak (maal w daulat ki kasarat ki wjah se ye haal na ho jaey ke) aik shakhs apna sadqa lekar talash karey lekin koi usey leney wala na miley. phir Allah Taala ke darmyan koi parda na hoga aur na tarjamani ke liye koi tarjuman hoga. phir Allah Taala usse poochhega ke kya maine tujhey duniya mein maal nahi diya tha? wo kahega ke haan diya tha. phir Allah Taala poochhega ke kya maine terey paas paighambar nahi bheja tha? wo kahega ke haan bheja tha. phir wo shakhs apne daain taraf dekhega to aag ke siwa aur kuchh nazar nahi aaeyga phir baain taraf dekhega aur idhar bhi aag hi aag hogi. to tumhen jahannam se darnaa chahiye chahe aik khajoor ke tukdey hi (ka sadqa karke usse apna bachao kar sako) agar ye bhi muyassar na aa sakey to achi baat hi munh se nikaaley."
1414,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke logon par zaroor aik zamana aisa aa jaeyga ke aik shakhs soney ka sadqa lekar niklega lekin koi usey leney wala nahi milega aur ye bhi hoga ke aik mard ki panah mein 40-40 auratein ho jaengi kyonke mardon ki kami ho jaeygi aur aurton ki zyadti hogi.
1415,jab aayate-sadqa nazil hui to ham bojh dhoney ka kaam kya kartey they (taake is tarah jo mazdoorii miley usey sadqa kar diya jaey) usi zamane mein aik shakhs (Abdur-Rehmaan-bin-Auf) aaya aur usne sadqe ke taur par kafi cheezein pesh kin. is par logon ne ye kehna shuru kya ke ye aadmi dikhaawaa karne waala hai. phir aik aur shakhs ( abu-Aqeel naam ke) aaya aur usne sirf aik saa ka sadqa kya. iske barey mein logon ne ye keh diya ke Allah Taala ko aik saa sadqe ki kya zarurat hai. is par ye aayat nazil huii الذين يلمزون المطوعين من المؤمنين في الصدقات والذين لا يجدون إلا جهدهم ''wo log jawan mominon par aib lagaatey hain jo sadqa zyada detey hain aur un par bhi jo mehnat se kamaa kar latey hain. (aur kam sadqa kartey hain) '' aakhir tak.
1416,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab hamein sadqa karne ka hukm diya to ham mein se bahut se bazar ja kar bojh uthaney ki mazdoorii kartey aur is tarah aik mudd (ghalla ya khajoor wghaira) hasil kartey. (jisey sadqa kar detey) lekin aaj ham mein se bahut son ke paas laakh-laakh (dirham ya diinaar) maujood hain.
1417,maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna ke jahannam se bacho agarche khajoor ka aik tukda de kar hi sahii ( magar zaroor sadqa karke dozakh ki aag se bchney ki koshish karo).
1418,aik aurat apni 2 bachchiyon ko liye maangtii hui aai. mere paas aik khajoor ke siwa us waqt aur kuchh na tha maine wahi de di. wo aik khajoor usne apni donon bachchiyon mein taqseem kar di aur khud nahi khaaii. phir wo uthi aur chali gaee. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey to maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se uska haal bayan kya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jisne un bachchiyon ki wjah se khud ko maamooli si bhi takleef mein daala to bachchiyaan uske liye dozakh se bachao ke liye aad bin jaaeingii.
1419,aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha ke ya Rasulullah ! kis tarah ke sadqe mein sabse zyada sawab hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us sadqe mein jisey tum sihat ke sath kanjoosii ke bawajud karo. tumhen aik taraf to faqeerii ka dar ho aur dusri taraf maaldaar banney ki tamanna aur ummeed ho aur (is sadqe-khairaat mein) dheel na honii chahiye ke jab jaan halaq tak aa jaey to us waqt to kehney lagey ke falan ke liye itna aur falan ke liye itna halanke wo to ab falan ka ho chukaa.
1420,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kuchh beeviyon ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke sabse pahley ham mein aakhirat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kon ja kar milegii to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jiska hath sabse zyada lamba hoga. ab ham ne lakdi se naapnaa shuru kar diya to Sauda (Raziallahu anha) sabse lambey hath wali niklin. ham ne baad mein samjha ke lambey hath wali honey se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki murad sadqa zyada karne wali se thi aur Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ham sabse pahley Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja kar miliin, sadqa karna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bahut mahboob tha."
1421,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ne ( Bani-Israeel mein se) kaha ke mujhey zaroor sadqa ( aaj raat ( dena hai. chunanche wo apna sadqa lekar nikla aur) naa-waaqifi se) aik chor ke hath mein rakh diya. subah hui to logon ne kehna shuru kya ke aaj raat kisi ne chor ko sadqa de diya. us shakhs ne kaha ke aey Allah ! tamam tareef terey hi liye hai. ( aaj raat ( main phir zaroor sadqa karunga. chunanche wo dobara sadqa lekar nikla aur us martaba aik faahisha ke hath mein de aaya. jab subah hui to phir logon mein charcha hua ke aaj raat kisi ne faahisha aurat ko sadqa de diya. us shakhs ne kaha aey Allah ! tamam tareef terey hi liye hai, main zaaniya ko apna sadqa de aaya. achchha aaj raat phir zaroor sadqa nikaalunga. chunanche apna sadqa liye huey wo phir nikla aur us martaba aik maaldaar ke hath par rakh diya. subah hui to logon ki zaban par zikr tha ke aik maaldaar ko kisi ne sadqa de diya hai. us shakhs ne kaha ke aey Allah ! hamd terey hi liye hai. main apna sadqa ( laa-ilmii se) chor, faahisha aur maaldaar ko de aaya. ( Allah Taala ki taraf se) bataya gaya ke jahan tak chor ke hath mein sadqa chaley janey ka sawal hai. to usmein iska imkan hai ke wo chori se ruk jaey. isi tarah faahisha ko sadqe ka maal mil janey par iska imkan hai ke wo zina se ruk jaey aur maaldaar ke hath mein pad janey ka ye fayda hai ke usey ibrat ho aur phir jo izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne usey diya hai, wo kharch kare."
1422,maine aur mere walid aur dada ( Akhfash bin Habib ( ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par bait ki thi. aap ne meri mangnii bhi karaai aur aap hi ne nikah bhi padhaayaa tha aur main aap ki khidmat mein aik muqaddima lekar hazir hua tha. wo ye ke mere walid Yazeed ne kuchh Dinar khairat ki niyat se nikaley aur unko unhon-ne masjid mein aik shakhs ke paas rakh diya. main gaya aur maine unko us se ley liya. phir jab main unhein lekar walid sahib ke paas aaya to unhon-ne farmaya ke qism Allah ki mera irada tujhey dene ka nahi tha. yahi muqaddima main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar hazir hua aur aap ne ye faisla diya ke dekho Yazeed jo tum ne niyat ki thi iska sawab tumhen mil gaya aur Ma'n (معن) ! jo to ne ley liya wo ab tera ho gaya.
1423,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya saat (7) qism ke aadmiyon ko Allah Taala apne ( arsh ke) saaye mein rakhega jis din iske siwa aur koi saaya na hoga. insaf karne wala Hakim , wo naujawaan jo Allah Taala ki ibadat mein jawan hua ho, wo shakhs jiska dil har waqt masjid mein laga rahe, 2 aisey shakhs jo Allah ke liye mohabbat rakhtey hain, usi par wo jama huey aur usi par juda huey, aisa shakhs jisey kisi khoobsurat aur izzat daar aurat ne bulaya lekin us ne ye jawab diya ke main Allah se darta hun, wo insan jo sadqa karey aur usey us darja chhipaaey ke baain hath ko bhi khabar na ho ke daahiney hath ne kya kharch kya aur wo shakhs jo Allah ko tanhai mein yad karey aur uski aankhen aansuon se bahney lag jaaein."
1424,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke sadqe kya karo to an-qareeb aik aisa zamana aaney wala hai jab aadmi apna sadqa lekar niklega (koii usey qabool kar ley magar jab wo kisi ko dega to wo) aadmi kahega ke agar isey tum kal laey hotey to main ley leta lekin aaj mujhey uski haajat nahi rahi."
1425,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya agar aurat apne shauhar ke maal se kuchh kharch karey aur uski niyat shauhar ki poonjii barbad karne ki na ho to usey kharch karne ka sawab milega aur shauhar ko bhi iska sawab milega usne kamaayaa hai aur khazaanchii ka bhi yahi hukm hai. aik ka sawab doosrey ke sawab mein koi kami nahi karta.
1426,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya behtreen khairat wo hai jiske dene ke baad aadmi maaldaar rahe. phir sadqa pahley unhein do jo tumhari zere-parwarish hain.
1427,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya uper wala hath nichey waley hath se behtar hai aur pahley unhein do jo tumharey baal bachchey aur azeez hain aur behtreen sadqa wo hai jisey de kar aadmi maaldaar rahe aur jo koi sawal se bachna chaahega usey Allah Taala bhi mehfooz rakhta hai aur jo dusron (ke maal) se be-niyaaz rehta hai, usey Allah Taala be-niyaaz hi bana deta hai."
1428,"aur Wuhaib ne bayan kya ke ham se Hisham ne apne walid se bayan kya, unse Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unse Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa hi bayan farmaayaa."
1429,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna. (doosri sanad) aur ham se Abdullaah-bin-Muslima ne bayan kya, unse Malik ne, unse Naafe ne aur unse Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jabke aap member par tashrif rakhtey they. aap ne sadqa aur kisi ke samney hath na phailaaney ka aur dusron se maangney ka zikr farmaya aur farmaya ke uper wala hath nichey waley hath se behtar hai. uper ka hath kharch karne waley ka hai aur nichey ka hath maangney waley kaa."
1430,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Asr ki Namaz ada ki phir jaldi se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghar mein tashrif ley gaey. thodi der baad bahar tashrif ley aaey. is par maine puchha ya kisi aur ne puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main ghar ke andar sadqe ke soney ka aik tukda chhod aaya tha mujhey ye baat pasand nahi aai ke usey taqseem kiye baghair raat guzaaroon to maine usko baant diya.
1431,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eid ke din nikley. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( eidgaah mein) 2 rakaat Namaz padhai. na Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se pahley koi Namaz padhi aur na iske ba'd. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ki taraf aaey. Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne waz (nasihat) w nasihat ki aur unko sadqa karne ke liye hukm farmaya, chunanche auratein kangan aur baaliyaan ( Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein) dalney lagiin ."
1432,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas agar koi maangney wala aata ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney koi haajat pesh ki jati to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sahaba kiram se farmatey ke tum sifarish karo ke iska sawab paogey aur Allah paak apne Nabi ki zaban se jo faisla chaahega wo dega.
1433,mujh se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khairat ko mat rok warna tera rizq bhi rok diya jaeyga
1434,wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan aaiin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke (maal ko) thaili mein band karke na rakhna warna Allah paak bhi tumharey liye apne khazaaney mein bandish laga dega. jahan tak ho sakey logon mein khair khairat taqseem karti reh.
1435,"fitne se mutaalliq Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis aap logon mein kis ko yad hai? Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha, main is tarah yad rakhta hun jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko bayan farmaya tha. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke tumhen iske bayan par jur'at hai. achchha to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fitnon ke barey mein kya farmaya tha? maine kaha ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha) insan ki aazmaish ( fitna ( iske khaandaan, aulad aur padausiyon mein hoti hai aur namaaz, sadqa aur achi baton ke liye logon ko hukm karna aur buri baton se mana karna us fitney ka kaffara bin jati hain. Aamash ne kaha abu-Waeil kabhi yun kehtey they. Namaz aur sadqa aur achi baton ka hukm dena buri baat se roknaa, ye us fitney ko mitaa dene waley nek kaam hain. phir us fitney ke mutaalliq umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke meri murad us fitne se nahi. main us fitney ke barey mein poochhna chahta hun jo samandar ki tarah thaathein maarta hua phailega. Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, maine kaha ke ameerul-momineen aap us fitney ki fikr na kijiye aap ke aur us fitna ke darmyan aik band darwaza hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ke wo darwaza tod diya jaeyga ya sirf khola jaeyga unhon-ne batlaya nahi balke wo darwaza tod diya jaeyga is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke jab darwaza tod diya jaeyga to phir kabhi bhi band na ho sakega abu-Waeil ne kaha ke haan, phir ham raub ki wjah se Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) se ye na poochh sakey ke wo darwaza kon hai? isliye ham ne Masruq se kaha ke tum poochho. unhon-ne kaha ke Masruq (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne puchha to Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke darwaze se murad khud umr (Raziallahu anhu) hi they. ham ne phir puchha to kya umr (Raziallahu anhu) jantey they ke aap ki murad kon thi? unhon-ne kaha haan jaisey din ke baad raat ke aaney ko jantey hain aur ye isliye ke maine jo hadis bayan ki wo ghalat nahi thi."
1436,"maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! un nek kaamon se mutaalliq aap kya farmatey hain jinhein main jahiliyat ke zamane mein sadqa, ghulam aazad karne aur sila rehmii ki sura mein kya karta tha. kya unka mujhey sawab milega? Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum apni un tamam nekiyon ke sath Islam laey ho jo pahley guzar chuki hain."
1437,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab biwi apne khawind ke khaney mein se kuchh sadqa karey aur uski niyat usey barbad karne ki nahi hoti to usey bhi iska sawab milta hai aur uske khawind ko kamaaney ka sawab milta hai. isi tarah khazaanchii ko bhi iska sawab milta hai.
1438,(khaazin) musalman amaanatdaar jo kuchh bhi kharch karta hai aur kuchh baar farmaya wo cheez poori tarah deta hai jiska usey sarmaaya ke Malik ki taraf se hukm diya gaya aur iska dil bhi usse khush hai aur usi ko diya hai jisey dene ke liye Malik ne kaha tha to wo dene wala bhi sadqa dene walon mein se aik hai.
1439,jab koi aurat apne shauhar ke ghar (ke maal ( se sadqa kare.
1440,jab biwi apne shauhar ke maal mein se kisi ko khilaey aur iska irada ghar ko bigadney ka bhi na ho to usey iska sawab milta hai aur shauhar ko bhi waisaa hi sawab milta hai aur khazaanchii ko bhi waisaa hi sawab milta hai. shauhar ko kamaaney ki wjah se sawab milta hai aur aurat ko kharch karne ki wjah se.
1441,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jab aurat apne ghar ke khaney ki cheez se Allah ki raah mein kharch karey aur uska irada ghar ko bigadney ka na ho to usey uska sawab milega aur shauhar ko kamaaney ka sawab milega, isi tarah khazaanchii ko bhi aisa hi sawab milega."
1442,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, koi din aisa nahi jata ke jab bandey subah ko uthtey hain to 2 Farishtey aasman se na utartey hun. aik farishta to ye kehta hai ke aey Allah ! kharch karne waley ko iska badla de. aur doosra kehta hai ke aey Allah ! ( mumsik (aur kanjoos ke maal ko talaf kar de."
1443,"kanjoos aur sadqa dene waley ki misal aisey 2 shakhson ki tarah hai jinke badan par lohey ke 2 kurtey hain. (doosri sanad) imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha aur ham se abul-Yamaan ne bayan kya, kaha ke hamein Shuaib ne khabar di, kaha ke hamein abu-Zinaad ne khabar di ke Abdullah-bin Hurmuz Aaraj ne unse bayan kya aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye kehtey suna ke kanjoos aur kharch karne waley ki misal aisey 2 shakhson ki si hai jinke badan par lohey ke 2 kurtey hon chhaatiyon se hanslii tak. kharch karne ka aadi kharch karta hai to uske tamam jism ko (wo kurta) chipa leta hai ya (raawii ne ye kaha ke) tamam jism par wo phail jata hai aur uski ungliyan usmein chhup jati hai aur chalney mein iske paon ka nishan mit'taa jata hai. lekin kanjoos jab bhi kharch karne ka irada karta hai to us kurtey ka har halqa apni jagah se chimat jata hai. kanjoos usey kushaada karne ki koshish karta hai lekin wo kushaada nahi ho paata. Abdullah-bin Taaus ke sath us hadis ko Hasan-bin-Muslim ne bhi Taaus se riwayat kya, usmein 2 kurtey hain."
1444,unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir yahi hadis bayan ki usmein 2 zirahein hain.
1445,har musalman par sadqa karna zaroori hai. logon ne puchha aey Allah ke nabii! agar kisi ke paas kuchh na ho? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir apne hath se kuchh kamaa kar khud ko bhi nafa pahunchaaey aur sadqa bhi kare. logon ne kaha agar uski taqat na ho? farmaya ke phir kisi zarooratmand faryaadii ki madad kare. logon ne kaha agar uski bhi taqat na ho. farmaya phir achi baat par amal karey aur buri baton se baaz rahe. iska yahi sadqa hai.
1446,"Naseeba naam ke aik Ansari aurat ke yahan kisi ne aik bakri bheji (ye Naseeba naam ke Ansari aurat khud umme-Atiya (Raziallahu anhu) hi ka naam hai). us bakri ka gosht unhon-ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan bhi bhej diya. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum kya ke tumharey paas khaney ko koi cheez hai? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke aur to koi cheez nahi albatta us bakri ka gosht jo Naseeba (Raziallahu anhu) ne bheja tha, wo maujood hai. is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wahi lao ab iska khana durust ho gaya."
1447,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke panch oont se kam mein zakat nahi aur panch auqiya se kam (chaandii) mein zakat nahi. isi tarah panch wasq se kam (ghall) mein zakat nahi.
1448,Abu-Bakar siddeeq (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein (apne daure-khilaafat mein farz zakat se mutaalliq hidayat detey huey) Allah aur rasool ke hukm ke mutabiq ye farman likha ke jiska sadqa Binte-Makhaaz (ek saal ki oontnii) tak pahunch gaya ho aur uske paas Binte-Makhaaz (ek saal ki oontnii) nahi balke Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) hai. to us se wahi ley liya jaeyga aur uske badle mein sadqa wsool karne wala bees dirham ya 2 bakriyan zayed dedega aur agar uske paas Binte-Makhaaz (ek saal ki oontnii) nahi hai balke ''ibne-Laboon'' hai to ye ''ibne-Laboon'' hi ley liya jaeyga aur is sura mein kuchh nahi diya jaeyga wo maada ya nar oont jo teesrey saal mein laga ho.
1449,"us waqt mein maujood tha jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutbe se pahley Namaz ( eid ( padhi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dekha ke aurton tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki awaz nahi pahunchii, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas bhi aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) they jo apna kapda phailaey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton ko waz (nasihat) sunaya aur unse sadqa karne ke liye farmaya aur auratein (apnaa sadqa Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ke kapdey mein) dalney lagiin. ye kehtey waqt Ayub ne apne kaan aur galey ki taraf ishara kya."
1450,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein wahi cheez likhi thi jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zaroori qarar diya tha. ye ke zakat (ki zyaadtii) ke khof se juda judaa maal ko yakjaa aur yakjaa maal ko judaa-judaa na kya jaey.
1451,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein farz zakat mein wahi baat likhi thi jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne muqarrar farmai thi usmein ye bhi likhwaayaa tha ke jab 2 Sharik hon to wo apna hisab barabar kar lein.
1452,"aik dehati ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hijrat ke mutaalliq puchha (yani ye ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ijazat dein to main Madina mein hijrat kar aaoon) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, afsos! uski to shaan badi hai. kya terey paas zakat dene ke liye kuchh oont hain jinki to zakat diya karta hai? usne kaha ke haan! is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir kya hai samandaron ke us paar (jis mulk main to rahe wahaan) amal karta reh Allah terey kisi amal ka sawab kam nahi karega."
1453,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unke paas farz zakat ke un fareezon ke mutaalliq likha tha jinka Allah ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko hukm diya hai. ye ke jiske oonton ki zakat ''Jiz'aa'' (4 saal ka oont ka bachcha) tak pahunch jaey aur wo ''Jiz'aa'' (4 saal ka oont ka bachcha) uske paas na ho balke ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) ho to us se zakat mein ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) hi ley liya jaeyga lekin iske sath 2 bakriyan bhi li jaaeingii, agar unke dene mein usey aasani ho warna bees dirham liye jaengey. (taake ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) ki kami poori ho jaey) aur agar kisi par zakat mein ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) wajib ho aur ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) uske paas na ho balke ''Jiz'aa'' (4 saal ka oont ka bachcha) ho to us se ''Jiz'aa'' (4 saal ka oont ka bachcha) hi ley liya jaeyga aur zakat wsool karne wala zakat dene waley ko bees dirham ya 2 bakriyan dega aur agar kisi par zakat ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) ke barabar wajib ho gaee aur uske paas sirf Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) hai to us se Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) ley li jaeygi aur zakat dene waley ko 2 bakriyan ya bees dirham sath main aur dene padengey aur agar kisi par zakat Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) wajib ho aur uske paas ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) ho to ''Hiqqa'' (3 saal ka oont ka bachcha) hi usse ley liya jaeyga aur is sura mein zakat wsool karne wala bees dirham ya 2 bakriyan zakat dene waley ko dega aur kisi ke paas zakat mein Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) wajib hua aur Binte-Laboon (do saal ki oontni) uske paas nahi balke Binte-Makhaaz (ek saal ki oontnii) hai to us se Binte-Makhaaz (ek saal ki oontnii) hi ley liya jaeyga lekin zakat dene wala iske sath bees dirham ya 2 bakriyan dega."
1454,Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab unhein Bahrain (ka Hakim bana kar) bheja to unko ye parwaana likh diyaa. shuru' Allah ke naam se jo bada meharban bahut hi zyada raham karne wala hai. ye zakat ka wo fareeza hai jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon ke liye farz qarar diya hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Allah Taala ne iska hukm diya. isliye jo shakhs musalmanon se us parwaane ke mutabiq zakat maangey to musalmanon ko usey de dena chahiye aur agar koi us se zyada maangey to hargiz na de. chobis ya us se kam oonton mein har panch oont par aik bakri deeni hogi. ( panch se kam mein kuchh nahi ( lekin jab oonton ki tadaad pachchis tak pahunch jaey to pachchis se paintees tak eik-eik baras ki ontni wajib hogi jo maadda hoti hai. jab oont ki tadaad chhatees tak pahunch jaey (to chhatees se) paintaalees tak 2 baras ki maadda wajib hogi. jab tadaad chhiyaalees tak pahunch jaey (to chhiyaalees se) sath tak mein teen baras ki ontni wajib hogi jo juftii ke qaabil hoti hai. jab tadaad iksath tak pahunch jaey (to iksath se) pachhattar tak char baras ki maada wajib hogi. jab tadaad 76 tak pahunch jaey (to 76 se) 90 tak 2-2 baras ki 2 oontniyan wajib hongii. jab tadaad 91 tak pahunch jaey to ( 91 se) 120 tak 3-3 baras ki 2 oontniyan wajib hongi jo juftii ke qaabil hun. phir aik 120 se bhi tadaad aagey badh jaey to har chalis (40) par 2 baras ki ontni wajib hogi aur har pachaas par aik teen baras ki. aur agar kisi ke paas char oont se zyada nahi to is par zakat wajib na hogi magar jab unka Malik apni khushi se kuchh de aur un bakriyon ki zakat jo (saal ke aksar hissey jangal ya maidan wghaira mein) char kar guzarti hain agar unki tadaad chalis (40) tak pahunch gaee ho to (chaalees se) 120 tak aik bakri wajib hogi aur jab aik so bees se tadaad badh jaey (to 120 se) se 200 tak 2 bakriyan wajib hongii. agar 200 se bhi tadaad badh jaey to (to 200 se) 300 tak teen bakriyan wajib hongi aur jab 300 se bhi tadaad aagey nikal jaey to ab har 100 par aik bakri wajib hogi. agar kisi shakhs ki charney wali bakriyan chalis (40) se aik bhi kam hon to un par zakat wajib nahi hogi magar apni khushi se Malik kuchh dena chahey to de sakta hai. aur chandi mein zakat chaaleeswaan hissey wajib hogi lekin agar kisi ke paas aik so nawwey (dirham) se zyada nahi hain to is par zakat wajib nahi hogi magar khushi se kuchh agar Malik dena chahey to aur baat hai.
1455,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke bayan kiye huey ehkaame-zakaat ke mutabiq likha ke zakat mein boodhey, aibii aur nar na liye jaaein, albatta agar sadqa wsool karne wala munasib samjhey to ley sakta hai."
1456,"Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke fauran baad zakat deney se inkar karne walon ke mutaalliq farmaya tha) qism Allah ki agar ye mujhey bakri ke aik bachche ko bhi deney se inkar karengey jisey ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko diya kartey they, to main unke us inkar par unse jihad karunga."
1457,iske siwa aur koi baat nahi thi jaisa ke main samajhta hun ke Allah Taala ne Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ko jihad ke liye Sina khol diya tha aur phir maine bhi yahi samjha ke faisla unhiin ka haq tha.
1458,jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko Yaman bheja to unse farmaya ke dekho ! tum aik aisi qaum ke paas ja rahe ho jo ahle-kitab ( Esai Yahudi ( hain. isliye sabse pahley unhein Allah ki ibadat ki dawat dena. jab wo Allah Taala ko pehchan lein (yani Islam qabool kar lein) to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne unke liye din aur raat mein panch namazein farz ki hain. jab wo usey bhi ada karein to unhein batana ke Allah Taala ne un par zakat farz qarar di hai jo unke sarmaayadaaron se li jaeygi (jo saahibe-nisaab hongey) aur unhiin ke faqeeron mein taqseem kar di jaeygi. jab wo usey bhi maan lein to unse zakat wsool kar. albatta unki umda cheezein ( zakat ke taur par leney se) parhez karna.
1459,panch wasq se kam khajooron mein zakat nahi aur panch auqiya se kam chandi mein zakat nahi. isi tarah panch oonton se kam mein zakat nahi hai.
1460,"main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahunch gaya tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qism is tarah khaaii) us zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi. ya jin alfaz ke sath bhi aap ne qism khaaii ho (is takeed ke baad farmaya) koi bhi aisa shakhs jiske paas oont, gaaey ya bakri ho aur wo iska haq ada na karta ho to qiyamat ke din usey laya jaeyga duniya se zyada badi aur motii taaza karke. phir wo apne Malik ko apne khuron se raundegii aur seeng maaregii. jab aakhiri janwar is par se guzar jaeyga to pahlaa janwar phir lot kar aaega. (aur usey apne seeng maarega aur khuron se raundega) us waqt tak (ye silsile barabar qaaim rahega) jab tak logon ka faisla nahi ho jata. us hadis ko Bukair bin-Abdullah ne Abu-Saleh se riwayat kya hai, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. baab apne rishte-daaron ko zakat dena aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zenab ke haq mein farmaya (jo Abdullah-bin-Masood ki biwi thi) usko 2 guna sawab milega, nataa jodney aur sadqey kaa."
1461,"abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Madina mein Ansar mein sabse zyada maaldaar they. apne khajoor ke baghaat ki wjah se. aur apne baghaat mein sabse zyada pasand unhein beerhaa ka baagh tha. ye baagh masjide-Nabawi ke bilkul samney tha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) usmein tashrif ley jaya kartey aur iska meethaa pani piyaa kartey they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jab ye aayat nazil huiin ( لن تنالوا البر حتى تنفقوا مما تحبون‏ ) yaanii ''tum neki ko us waqt tak nahi pa saktey jab tak tum apni pyari se pyari cheez na kharch karo.'' ye sun kar abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke aey Allah ke rasool! Allah tabarak w taala farmata hai ke tum us waqt tak neki ko nahi pa saktey jab tak tum apni pyari se pyari cheez na kharch karo aur mujhey beerhaa ka baagh sabse zyada pyara hai. isliye main usey Allah Taala ke liye khairat karta hun. uski neki aur uske zakheera aakhirat honey ka ummeedwaar hun. Allah ke hukm se jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) munasib samjhein usey istemal keejiye. rawi ne bayan kya ke ye sun kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, khub ! ye to bada hi aamadni ka maal hai. ye to bahut hi nafa-bakhsh hai. aur jo baat tum ne kahi maine wo sun li aur main munasib samajhta hun ke tum usey apne nazdeekii rishte-daaron ko de daalo. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ya Rasulullah! main aisa hi karunga. chunanche unhon-ne usey apne rishte-daaron aur chacha ke ladkon ko de diya. Abdullah-bin Yusuf ke sath is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Rooh ne ki hai. Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Ismail ne Malik ke waaste se ( رابح (ke bajaey ( رائح ( naql kya hai."
1462,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) eidul-Azha ya eidul-fitr mein eidgaah tashrif ley gaey. phir (namaz ke baad) logon ko waz (nasihat) farmaya aur sadqe ka hukm diya. farmaya : logo ! sadqa do. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aurton ki taraf gaey aur unse bhi yahi farmaya ke aurton ! sadqa do ke maine jahannam mein kasrat se tum hi ko dekha hai. aurton ne puchha ke ya Rasulullah ! aisa kyon hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, isliye ke tum la'an-ta'an zyada karti ho aur apne shauhar ki na-shukri karti ho. maine tum se zyada aql aur Deen ke eitibaar se naaqis aisi koi makhlooq nahi dekhi jo kaar aazmooda mard ki aql ko bhi apni muththii mein ley leti ho. haan aey aurto! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas ghar pahunchey to ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi Zenab (Raziallahu anha) aaiin aur ijazat chaahi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke ye Zenab aai hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kon si Zenab (kyonke Zenab naam ki bahut si auratein thiin) kaha gaya ke ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki beewii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, achchha unhein ijazat de do, chunanche ijazat de di gaee. unhon-ne aa kar arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! aaj aap ne sadqe ka hukm diya tha aur mere paas bhi kuchh zewar hai jisey main sadqa karna chahti thi. lekin) mere khawind ( ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ye khayal kartey hain ke wo aur unke ladkey iske un ( miskinon ( se zyada mustahiq hain jin par main sadqa karoongii. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne sahi kaha, tumharey shauhar aur tumharey ladkey us sadqe ke unse zyada mustahiq hain jinhein tum sadqe ke taur par dogii. (ma'loom hua ke aqaarib agar mohtaaj hon to sadqe ke awwaleen mustahiq wahi hain)."
1463,musalman par uske ghodey aur ghulam ki zakat wajib nahi.
1464,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya musalman par na uske ghulam mein zakat farz hai aur na ghodey mein.
1465,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din member par tashrif farma huey. ham bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ird-gird baith gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey mutaalliq is baat se darta hun ke tum par duniya ki khush'haalii aur uski banaaw-singaar ke darwazey khol diye jaengey. aik shakhs ne arz kya. ya Rasulullah ! kya achai burai paida karegii? is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khamosh ho gaey. isliye us shakhs se kaha janey laga ke kya baat thi. tum ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik baat poochhi lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum se baat nahi kartey. phir ham ne mehsus kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. bayan kya ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne paseena saaf kya (jo wahiy nazil hotey waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko aaney lagta tha) phir puchha ke sawal karne waley sahib kahan hain. ham ne mehsus kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske (sawaal ki) tareef ki. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achai burai nahi paida karti (magar be mauqa istemal se burai paida hoti hai) kyonke mausame-bahaar mein kuchh aisi ghaas bhi ugtii hain jo jaan lewaa ya takleef deh Sabit hoti hain. albatta hariyaalii charney wala wo janwar bach jata hai ke khub chartaa hai aur jab uski donon kokhein bhar jati hain to suraj ki taraf rukh karke pakhana peshab kar deta hai aur phir chartaa hai. isi tarah ye maal w daulat bhi aik khushgawaar hariyaalii hai. aur musalman ka wo maal kitna umda hai jo miskeen, yateem aur musaafir ko diya jaey. ya jis tarah Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya, haan agar koi shakhs zakat haqdaar honey ke baghair leta hai to uski misal aisey shakhs ki si hai jo khata hai lekin uska pet nahi bharta aur qiyamat ke din ye maal uske khilaf gawah hoga."
1466,"mein masjide-Nabawi mein thi. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko maine dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye farma rahe they, sadqa karo, chahe apne zewar hi mein se do aur Zenab apna sadqa apne shauhar Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) aur chand yatimon par bhi jo unki parwarish mein they kharch kya karti thin. isliye unhon-ne apne khawind se kaha ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochhiye ke kya wo sadqa bhi mujh se kifaayat karega jo main aap par aur un chand yatimon par kharch karun jo meri sipurdagii mein hain. lekin Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke tum khud ja kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se poochh lo. aakhir main khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui. us waqt maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke darwazey par aik Ansari khatun ko paya. jo meri hi jaisi zarurat lekar maujood thin. (jo Zenab Abu-Masood Ansari ki biwi thiin) phir hamarey samney se Bilal guzrey . to ham ne unse kaha ke aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye masla malum kijiye ke kya wo sadqa mujh se kifaayat karega jisey main apne shauhar aur apni zere-tahweel kuch yateem bachchon par kharch kar dun. ham ne Bilal se ye bhi kaha ke hamara naam na lenaa. wo andar gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke 2 auratein masla malum karti hain. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye donon kon hain? Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne keh diya ke Zenab naam ki hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kon si Zainab? Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan! beshak durust hai. aur unhein do guna sawab milega. aik rishtedaarii ka aur doosra khairat karne kaa."
1467,"maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! agar main abu-Salma (apne pahley khawind (ke beton par kharch karun to durust hai ya nahi. kyonke wo meri bhi aulad hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, un par kharch kar. to jo kuchh bhi un par kharch karegi iska sawab tujh ko milega."
1468,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zakat wsool karne ka hukm diya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke ibne-Jameel aur Khalid-bin Waleed aur Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib ne zakat deney se inkar kar diya hai. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ibne-Jameel ye shukr nahi karta ke kal tak wo faqeer tha. phir Allah ne apne rasool ki dua ki barkat se usey maaldaar bana diya. baqi rahe Khalid, to un par tum log zulm kartey ho. unhon-ne to apni zirahein Allah Taala ke rastey mein waqf kar rakhi hain. aur Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib, to wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacha hain. aur unki zakat unhi par sadqa hai. aur itna hi aur unhein meri taraf se dena hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Zinaad ne apne walid se ki aur ibne-Ishaq ne abu-Zinaad se ye alfaz bayan kiye. ( هي عليه ومثلها معها ( ) sadqe ke lafz ke baghair (aur ibne-Juraij ne kaha ke mujh se Aaraj se isi tarah ye hadis bayan ki gaee."
1469,Ansar ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se sawal kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein diya. phir unhon-ne sawal kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir diya. yahan tak ke jo maal Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tha. ab wo khatm ho gaya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar mere paas jo maal w daulat ho to main usey bacha kar nahi rakhoonga . magar jo shakhs sawal karne se bachta hai to Allah Taala bhi usey sawal karne se mehfooz hi rakhta hai. aur jo shakhs be-niyaazii barat'taa hai to Allah Taala usey be-niyaaz bana deta hai aur jo shakhs apne uper zor daal kar bhi sabr karta hai to Allah Taala bhi usey sabr w istiqlaal de deta hai. aur kisi ko bhi sabr se zyada behtar aur usse zyada be-paayaan khair nahi milii. (sabr tamam ne'maton se badh kar hai).
1470,us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar koi shakhs rassii se lakdiyon ka bojh baandh kar apni peeth par jangal se utha laey ( phir unhein bazar mein bech kar apna rizq hasil karey) to wo us shakhs se behtar hai jo kisi ke paas aa kar sawal kare. phir jis se sawal kya gaya hai wo usey de ya na de.
1471,"tum mein se koi bhi agar (zarooratmand ho to) apni rassii lekar aaey aur lakdiyon ka gathaa baandh kar apni peeth par rakh kar laey aur usey bechey. is tarah Allah Taala uski izzat ko mehfooz rakh ley to ye us se achchha hai ke wo logon se sawal karta phirey, usey wo dein ya na dein."
1472,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kuchh maanga . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ata farmaya. maine phir maanga aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir ata farmaya. maine phir maanga Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir bhi ata farmaya. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya, aey hakeem! ye daulat badi sar-sabz aur bahut hi sheereen hai. lekin jo shakhs usey dene aur ata karne ki niyat k sath ley to uski daulat mein barkat hoti hai. aur jo laalach ke sath leta hai to uski daulat mein kuchh bhi barkat nahi hogi. uska haal us shakhs jaisa hoga jo khata hai lekin aasooda nahi hota (yaad rakho) uper ka hath nichey ke hath se behtar hai. Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, ke maine kaha us zaat ki qasam! jisne aapko sachchai ke sath Nabi banaakar bheja hai. ab iske baad mein kisi se koi cheez nahi loonga. yahan tak ke us duniya hi se main juda ho jaun. chunanche Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hakeem (Raziallahu anhu) ko unka mamool (routine) dene ko bulatey to wo leney se inkar kar detey. phir umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi unhein unka hissey dena chaha to unhon-ne iske leney se inkar kar diya. is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke musalmaanon! main tumhen Hakeem-bin-Hizaam ke maamle mein gawah banata hun ke maine unka haq unhein dena chaha lekin unhon-ne leney se inkar kar diya. gharaz Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad isi tarah kisi se bhi koi cheez leney se hamesha inkar hi kartey rahe. yahan tak ke wafat pa gaey. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ''maale-fae'' yani mulkii aamadni se unka hissey unko dena chahtey they magar unhon-ne wo bhi nahi liya."
1473,"maine umr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo kehtey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujhey koi cheez ata farmatey to main arz karta ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mujh se zyada mohtaaj ko de dijiye. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmatey ke lelo, agar tumhen koi aisa maal miley jis par tumhara khayal na laga hua ho aur na tum ne usey maanga ho to usey qabool kar liya karo aur jo na miley to uski parwah na karo aur uske peechhey na pado."
1474,aadmi hamesha logon ke samney hath phailaataa rehta hai yahan tak ke wo qiyamat ke din is tarah uthega ke iske chehrey par zara bhi gosht na hoga.
1475,"qiyamat ke din suraj itna qareeb ho jaeyga ke paseena aadhey kaan tak pahunch jaeyga log usi haal main apni mukhlisii ke liye Adam (Alaihissalam) se faryaad karengey. phir Musa (Alaihissalam) se. aur phir Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se. Abdullah ne apni riwayat mein ye zyadti ki hai ke mujh se Leis ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se ibn-abii-Ja'far ne bayan kya, ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shafaat karengey ke makhlooq ka faisla kya jaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) badhengey aur jannat ke darwazey ka halqa thaam lengey aur isi din Allah Taala aapko ''maqaame-mahmood'' ata farmaeyga. jiski tamam ahale-mahshar tareef karengey aur muallaa-bin-Asad ne kaha ke ham se Wuhaib ne Naumaan-bin-Raashid se bayan kya, unse Zohri ke bhai Abdullaah-bin-Muslim ne, unse Hamza bin-Abdullah ne, aur unhon-ne Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se phir itni hi hadis bayan ki jo sawal ke baab mein hai."
1476,maine Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya miskeen wo nahi jisey 1-2 luqmey dar-dar phiraaiin. miskeen to wo hai jiske paas maal nahi. lekin usey sawal se sharm aati hai aur wo logon se chimat kar nahi mangta ( miskeen wo jo kamaaey magar baqadr zarurat na pa sakey ( .
1477,"Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ne Mughira-bin-Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) ko likha ke unhein koi aisi hadis likhiye jo aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suni ho. Mughira (Raziallahu anhu) ne likha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala tumharey liye teen baatein pasand nahi karta. bila wajah ki gap-shap, fuzool kharchi aur logon se bahut maangnaa."
1478,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand ashkhaas ko kuchh maal diya. usi jagah main bhi betha hua tha. unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke sath hi baithey huey shakhs ko chhod diya aur unhein kuchh nahi diya. halanke un logon mein wahi mujhey zyada pasand tha. aakhir maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb ja kar chupkey se arz kya, falan shakhs ko aap ne kuchh bhi nahi diya ? Allah ki qism main usey momin khayal karta hun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ya musalman? unhon-ne bayan kya ke is par main thodi der tak khamosh raha. lekin main unke mutaalliq jo kuchh janta tha usne mujhey majbur kya, aur maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! aap falan shakhs se kyon khafa hain, Allah ki qism ! main usey momin samajhta hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ya musalman ? teen martaba aisa hi hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik shakhs ko deta hun (aur doosrey ko nazar andaz kar jata hun) halanke wo doosra meri nazar mein pahley se zyada pyara hota hai. kyonke (jis ko main deta hun na dene ki sura mein) mujhey dar is baat ka rehta hai ke kahin usey chehrey ke bal ghaseet kar jahannam mein na daal diya jaey. aur (ya'qoob-bin-Ibraaheem (Alaihissalam) ( apne walid se, wo Saleh se, wo Ismaaeel-bin-Muhammad se, unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine apne walid se suna ke wo yahi hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna hath meri gardan aur mundhey ke beech mein maara aur farmaya, Sad! idhar suno. main aik shakhs ko deta hun. aakhir hadis tak. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke) Quran Majeed mein lafz ( ) كبكبوا‏ ( aundhey lita dene ke mana mein hai. aur sura Mulk mein jo ( مكبا‏ (ka lafz hai wo ( أكب ( se nikla hai. ( أكب ( lazim hai yani aundha gira aur iska mutaaddii ( كب ( hai. kehtey hain ke) كبه الله لوجهه ( yani Allah ne usey aundhey munh gira diya aur) كببته ( yani maine usko aundha giraayaa. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha Saleh bin kaisaan umr mein Zohri se badey they wo Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se miley hain."
1479,miskeen wo nahi hai jo logon ka chakkar kaat'taa phirtaa hai taake usey 2-1 luqma ya 2-1 khajoor mil jaaein. balke aslii miskeen wo hai jiske paas itna maal nahi ke wo iske zariey se be-parwaah ho jaey. us haal mein bhi kisi ko malum nahi ke koi usey sadqa hi dedey aur na wo khud hath phailaaney ke liye uthtaa hai.
1480,agar tum mein se koi shakhs apni rassii lekar (meraa khayal hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun farmaya) pahadon mein chala jaey phir lakdiyan jama karke unhein bechey. usse khaaey bhi aur sadqa bhi kare. ye uske liye usse behtar hai ke logon ke samney hath phailaaey.
1481,"ham ghazwae-tabook ke liye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ja rahe they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wadi Quraa (Madina Munawra aur Sham (Syria) ke darmyan aik qadeem aabadi) se guzrey to hamari nazar aik aurat par padi jo apne baagh mein khadi hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke iske phalon ka andaza lagaao (ke usmein kitni khajoor niklegii) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne das wasq ka andaza lagaya. phir us aurat se farmaya ke yad rakhna usmein se jitni khajoor nikley. jab ham Tabook pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aaj raat badey zor ki aandhii chalegii isliye koi shakhs khada na rahe aur jiske paas oont hon to wo usey baandh dein. chunanche ham ne oont baandh liye aur aandhii badey zor ki aai. aik shakhs khada hua tha. to hawa ne usey ''Jabale-tay'' par ja phainkaa aur iila ke Hakim (Yuhanna-bin-Rooba) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko safaid khachchar aur aik chadar ka tohfa bhejaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tahreerii taur par usey uski hukumat par bar-qaraar rakha phir jab waadiie-Quraa (waapsii mein) pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usi aurat se puchha ke tumharey baagh mein kitna phal aaya tha usne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke andaaze ke mutabiq das wasq aaya tha. iske baad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Madina jald jana chahta hun. isliye jo koi mere sath jaldi chalnaa chahey wo mere sath jald rawaana ho phir jab ( ibne-bakkaar imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke Shekh ne aik aisa jumla kaha jiske matlab ye they) ke Madina dikhai dene laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye hai taaba ! phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud pahaad dekha to farmaya ke ye pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham bhi us se mohabbat rakhtey hain. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya main Ansar ke sabse achchhey khandan ki nishaandehi na karun? sahaba ne kaha ke zaroor keejiye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke banu-Najjaar ka khaandaan. phir bano abdul-Ash'hal ka khaandaan, phir banu-Saaida ka ya (ye farmaya ke) bani Haaris-bin-Khazraj ka khandan aur farmaya ke Ansar ke tamam hi khandanon mein khair hai, abu-Adbullah (qaasim-bin-Salaam) ne kaha ke jis baagh ki chaar diwari ho usey hadeeqa kahengey aur jiski chaar diwari na ho usey hadeeqa nahi kahengey."
1482,Uhud wo pahaad hai jo ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain.
1483,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, wo zameen jisey aasman ( barish ka pani (ya chashma sairaab karta ho. ya wo khud-b-khud nami se sairaab ho jati ho to uski paidawar se daswaan hissey liya jaey aur wo zameen jisey kuwein se pani kheench kar sairaab kya jata ho to uski paidawar se beeswaan hissey liya jaey. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke ye hadis yani Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis ke jis kheti mein aasman ka pani diya jaey, daswaan hissa hai pehli hadis yani abu-Saeed ki hadis ki tafseer hai. usmein zakat ki koi miqdar ka zikr nahi hai aur ismein zikr hai. aur zyadti qabool ki jati hai. aur gol-mol hadis ka hukm saaf-saaf hadis ke muwafiq liya jata hai. jab iska rawi qaabile-bharosa ho. jaisey Fazal-bin-Abbaas (Raziallahu anhu) ne riwayat kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Kaba mein Namaz nahi padhi. lekin Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ne batlaya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz ( Kaba mein) padhi thi. us mauqe par bhi Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat qabool ki gaee aur Fazal (Raziallahu anhu) ka qaul chhod diya gaya."
1484,"panch wasq se kam mein zakat nahi hai, aur panch mahaar oonton se kam mein zakat nahi hai. aur chandi ke panch auqiya se kam mein zakat nahi hai."
1485,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas todney ke waqt zakat ki khajoor laai jaatii, har shakhs apni zakat laataa aur naubat yahan tak pahunchti ke khajoor ka aik dher lag jata. (eik martaba ( Hasan aur Husain (Raziallahu anhu) aisi hi khajooron se khel rahe they ke aik ne aik khajoor utha kar apne munh mein rakh li. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jaise hi dekha to unke munh se wo khajoor nikal li aur farmaya ke kya tumhen malum nahi ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aulad zakat ka maal nahi kha saktii."
1486,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khajoor ko) darakht par) us waqt tak bechney se mana farmaya hai jab tak uski pukhtagi zahir na ho. aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se jab poochhtey ke uski pukhtagi kya hai, wo kehtey ke jab ye malum ho jaey ke ab ye phal aafat se bach rahega."
1487,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phal ko us waqt tak bechney se mana farmaya jab tak unki pukhtagi khul na jaey.
1488,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab tak phal par surkhi na aa jaey, unhein bechney se mana farmaya hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke murad ye hai ke jab tak wo paak kar surkh na ho jaaein."
1489,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik ghoda Allah ke raaste mein sadqa kya. phir usey aap ne dekha ke wo bazar mein bik raha hai. isliye unki khahish hui ke usey wo khud hi khareed lein aur ijazat leney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apna sadqa wapas na lo. isi wjah se agar ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) apna diya hua koi sadqa khareed letey, to phir usey sadqa kar detey they. (apne istemal mein na rakhtey they. baab aur hadis mein mutaabiqat zahir hai)."
1490,unhon-ne aik ghoda Allah Taala ke raaste mein aik shakhs ko sawari ke liye de diya. lekin us shakhs ne ghodey ko kharaab kar diya. isliye maine chaha ke usey khareed loon. mera ye bhi khayal tha ke wo usey sastey daamon beech daalega . chunanche maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke apna sadqa wapas na lo. chahe wo tumhen aik dirham hi mein kyon na de kyonke diya hua sadqa wapas leney waley ki misal qai karke chaatney waley ki si hai.
1491,"Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne zakat ki khajooron ke dher se aik khajoor utha kar apne munh mein daal li to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, chhii chhii ! nikaalo usey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kya tumhen malum nahi ke ham log sadqe ka maal nahi khaatey ."
1492,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Memuna (Raziallahu anha) ki baandi ko jo bakri sadqe mein kisi ne di thi wo mari hui dekhi. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log iske chamdey ko kyon nahi kaam mein laey. logon ne kaha ke ye to murda hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haram to sirf iska khana hai.
1493,"unka irada hua ke Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko (jo baandi thiin) aazad kar dene ke liye khareed lein. lekin iske asl Malik ye chahtey they ke 'walaa' unhiin ke liye rahe. iska zikr Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kya. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum khareed kar aazad kar do, 'walaa' to usi ki hoti hai, jo aazad kare. unhon-ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein gosht pesh kya gaya. maine kaha ke ye Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko kisi ne sadqe ke taur par diya hai to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye unke liye sadqa tha. lekin ab hamarey liye ye hadiya hai."
1494,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan tashrif laey aur malum farmaya ke kya tumharey paas kuchh hai? Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne jawab diya ke nahi koi cheez nahi. haan Naseeba (Raziallahu anhu) ka bheja hua us bakri ka gosht hai jo unhein sadqe ke taur par mili hai. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya lao khairat to apne thikaaney pahunch gaee.
1495,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein wo gosht pesh kya gaya jo Barira (Raziallahu anhu) ko sadqe ke taur par mila tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ko ye gosht un par sadqa tha. lekin hamarey liye ye hadiya hai. Abu-Dawud ne kaha ke hamein Shoba ne khabar di. unhein Qatada ne ke unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kartey they.
1496,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Yaman bheja , to unse farmaya ke tum aik aisi qaum ke paas ja rahe ho jo ahle-kitab hain. isliye jab tum wahan pahuncho to pahley unhein dawat do ke wo is baat ki gawahi dein ke Allah ke siwa koi maabood nahi aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Allah ke sachey rasool hain. wo is baat mein jab tumhari baat maan lein to unhein bataao ke Allah Taala ne un par rozaana din raat mein panch waqt ki namazein farz ki hain. jab wo tumhari ye baat bhi maan lein to unhein bataao ke unke liye Allah Taala ne zakat dena zaroori qarar diya hai, ye unke maaldaaron se li jaeygi aur unke ghareebon par kharch ki jaeygi. phir jab wo usmein bhi tumhari baat maan lein to unke achchhey maal leney se bacho aur mazloom ki aah se daro ke iske aur Allah Taala ke darmyan koi rukawat nahi hoti ."
1497,"jab koi qaum apni zakat lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hoti to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke liye dua farmaatey اللهم صل على آل فلانaey Allah ! aal falan ko khair w barkat ata farma, mere walid bhi apni zakat lekar hazir huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaayaa اللهم صل على آل أبي أوفىaey Allah ! aale-abi-Aufii ko khair w barkat ata farmaa."
1498,"Bani-Israeel mein aik shakhs tha jisne doosrey Bani-Israeel ke shakhs se hazaar ashrafiyaan qarz maangiin. us ne Allah ke bharosey par usko de dein. ab jisne qarz liya tha wo samandar par gaya ke Sawar ho jaey aur qarz-khaah ka qarz ada karey lekin sawari na mili . aakhir usne qarz-khaah tak pahunchne se naa-ummeed ho kar aik lakdi li usko kureda aur hazaar ashrafiyaan usmein bhar kar wo lakdi samandar mein phenk di. ittifaq se qarz-khaah kaam kaaj ko bahar nikla, samandar par pahuncha to aik lakdi dekhi aur usko ghar mein jalaaney ke khayal se ley aaya. phir poori hadis bayan ki. jab lakdi ko chira to usmein ashrafiyaan paaein ."
1499,janwar se jo nuqsan pahunchey iska kuchh badla nahi aur kuwein ka bhi yahi haal hai aur kaan ka bhi yahi hukm hai aur rikaaz mein se panchwan hissey liya jaey.
1500,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bani Asad ke aik shakhs Abdullaah-bin-Lutbiya ko banii-Sulaim ki zakat wsool karne par muqarrar farmaya, jab wo aaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse hisab liya."
1501,Uraina ke kuchh logon ko Madina ki aab w hua muwafiq nahi aai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein uski ijazat de di ke wo zakat ke oonton mein ja kar unka doodh aur peshab istemal karein (kyonke wo aisey marz mein mubtala they jiski dawaa yahi thi) lekin unhon-ne (un oonton ke) charwaahey ko mar daala aur oonton ko lekar bhag nikley. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke peechhey aadmi daudaaey aakhir wo log pakad laey gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke hath aur paon katwaa diye aur unki aankhon mein garm slaaiyaan phirwaa diin phir unhein dhoop mein dalwaa diya (jiski shiddat ki wjah se) wo patthar chabaaney lagey they. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) abu-Qilaba Sabit aur Humaid ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ke waaste se ki hai.
1502,mein Abdullah-bin-Ubai Talha ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki tehneek kar dein. (yani apne munh se koi cheez chabaa kar unke munh mein daal dein ( maine us waqt dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath mein dagh lagaaney ka aala tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zakat ke oonton par dagh laga rahe they.
1503,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fitr ki zakat ( sadqa fitr ( aik saa khajoor ya aik saa jau farz qarar di thi. ghulam , aazad , mard , aurat , chhotey aur badey tamam musalmanon par. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hukm ye tha ke Namaz ( eid (ke liye janey se pahley ye sadqa ada kar diya jaey."
1504,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fitr ki zakat aazad ya ghulaam, mard ya aurat tamam musalmanon par aik saa khajoor ya jau farz ki thi."
1505,ham aik saa ''jau'' ka sadqa diya kartey they.
1506,ham fitra ki zakat aik saa anaaj ya gehun ya aik saa jau ya aik saa khajoor ya aik saa paneer ya aik saa zubaib ( khushk angoor ya injeer) nikala kartey they.
1507,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik saa khajoor ya aik saa jau ki zakat fitr dene ka hukm farmaya tha. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir logon ne usi ke barabar 2 mudd (aadhaa saa ( gehun kar liya tha.
1508,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein sadqa fitr aik saa gehun ya aik saa khajoor ya aik saa jau ya aik saa '' zubaib '' ( khushk angoor ya khushk injeer) nikaaltey they. phir jab Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Madina mein aaey aur gehun ki aamadni hui to kehney lagey mein samajhta hun iska aik mudd doosrey anaaj ke 2 mudd ke barabar hai.
1509,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sadqa fitr Namaz ( eid (ke liye janey se pahley pahley nikalney ka hukm diya tha.
1510,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein eidul-fitr ke din (khaaney ke ghalla se) aik saa nikaaltey they. abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke hamara khana (un dinon ( jau , zubaib , paneer aur khajoor tha."
1511,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sadqa fitr ya ye kaha ke sadqae-ramazaan mard, aurat, aazad aur ghulam (sab par) aik saa khajoor ya aik saa jau farz qarar diya tha. phir logon ne aadha saa gehun iske barabar qarar de liya. lekin ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) khajoor diya kartey they. aik martaba Madina mein khajoor ka qahat padaa to aap ne jo sadqe mein nikaalaa. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) chhotey badey sab ki taraf se yahan tak ke mere beton ki taraf se bhi sadqa fitr nikaaltey they. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) sadqae-fitr har faqeer ko jo usey qabool karta, de diya kartey they. aur log sadqa fitr aik ya 2 din pahley hi de diya kartey they. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha mere beton se Naafe ke betey murad hain. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha wo eid se pahley jo sadqa de detey they, to ikattha honey ke liye na faqeeron ke liye (phir wo jama karke faqeeron mein taqseem kar diya jaataa)."
1512,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik saa jau ya aik saa khajoor ka sadqae-fitr, chhotey, badey, aazad aur ghulam sab par farz qarar diya."
